  "body": "From here: https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/pull/5884#issuecomment-1148970710\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/2522130/172581499-26a69088-265b-4546-81cb-a78be525f01d.png)\r\n\r\nModal should go to the full height of the window (but with a 64px margin top and bottom) if the window isn't tall enough to display the modal content without scrolling (which will almost always be the case with this modal, unless a user is using a monitor in portrait mode or something like that).\r\n\r\nThis same behaviour should apply to most tall modals in status desktop",
